WEBVTT

00:02:28.420 --> 00:02:31.686
kwa wale ambao tulizaliwa nyeti sana.

00:02:31.710 --> 00:02:34.574
Ni vigumu sana na ni ajabu
kwamba wakati mwingine tunajiuliza

00:02:34.598 --> 00:02:36.034
kama tunataniwa.

00:02:37.002 --> 00:02:41.956
Imejazwa na wema na uzuri wa umbo,

00:02:41.980 --> 00:02:43.755
umasikini,

00:02:43.779 --> 00:02:47.323
Mafuriko na watoto na chunusi na Mozart,

00:02:47.347 --> 00:02:49.486
vyote vilibiringizwa pamoja.

00:02:49.510 --> 00:02:52.080
Sidhani ni mfumo mzuri.

00:02:52.104 --> 00:02:55.420
(Vicheko)

00:02:55.444 --> 00:02:58.839
Namba mbili: karibia kila kitu kitafanya kazi tena

00:02:58.863 --> 00:03:01.204
ukikichomoa kwa dakika chache --